---
/**
 * Sales Letter Page (once.com/writebook style)
 * Two-column: 760px content left, ~340px sticky CTA card right
 * Simple nav bar, no floating capsule
 * Mobile: single column + sticky bottom button → expanding form sheet
 */
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '@/components/layout/Header.astro';
import LeadCaptureForm from '@/components/forms/LeadCaptureForm.tsx';
import MobileFormSheet from '@/components/forms/MobileFormSheet.tsx';
import siteConfig from '@/config/site.config';

const formTags = ['funnel_blueprint', 'sales_letter'];
const termsHtml = `<p>By providing my information, I agree to receive communications and accept the <a href="/terms">Privacy Policy</a>. Unsubscribe anytime.</p>`;
---

<BaseLayout
  title="The $100K Funnel Blueprint — Build Funnels That Print Money"
  description="The exact funnel system that generated $12M+ in revenue. Proven templates, automation sequences, and step-by-step playbooks. Free download."
>
  <Header slot="header" layout="minimal" position="fixed" variant="solid" size="lg">
    <span slot="actions" class="text-xs font-bold tracking-wide text-brand-500 uppercase">100% Free</span>
  </Header>

  {/* ── Two-column layout ── */}
  <div class="sl-layout">

    {/* ══ LEFT: content ══ */}
    <div class="sl-content">

      {/* Hero */}
      <header class="sl-hero">
        <h1 class="sl-title">
          The $100K Funnel<br class="hidden sm:inline" /> Blueprint
        </h1>

        <p class="sl-subtitle">
          Instantly build automated funnels that convert cold traffic into
          paying customers, no agency required. And you get the templates, too.
        </p>
      </header>

      {/* Editorial content */}
      <article class="sales-letter">

        <p>
          Building funnels from scratch is hard. But why is it still so hard to build a
          funnel that actually converts? It's not anymore.
          The $100K Funnel Blueprint is remarkably simple: proven templates, tested
          sequences, and step-by-step playbooks in a ready-to-deploy format.
        </p>

        <p>
          Here's <a href="#testimonials">what people are saying</a>. And <a href="#faq">the FAQ</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>Here's exactly what you get</h2>

        <p>
          The difference between a business doing $5K/month and one doing $100K/month
          usually isn't the product, the team, or even the traffic. It's <strong>the funnel</strong>.
          Specifically, it's whether you have a system that takes a complete stranger and
          walks them through a predictable, automated journey that ends with their credit
          card on your checkout page.
        </p>

        <p>
          Most businesses don't have this. They have a website with a "Contact Us"
          button and hope for the best. This isn't a course. There's no 40-hour video
          library or private Facebook group. It's a system — the actual assets and
          templates we use — packaged so you can deploy them in a weekend.
        </p>

        {/* Product screenshot — full width like once.com */}
        <figure class="sl-figure">
          <div class="sl-product-frame">
            <img
              src="/images/product-mockup.webp"
              alt="The $100K Funnel Blueprint — ebook bundle"
              width="1173"
              height="1410"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <figcaption>Everything you need: templates, sequences, workflows, and implementation guide.</figcaption>
        </figure>

        <h3>High-Converting Page Templates</h3>
        <p>
          Squeeze pages, sales pages, order forms, upsell pages, and thank-you pages.
          Every template has been A/B tested across thousands of visitors. You swap in
          your copy, your logo, your colors — and publish. These templates alone have
          generated millions in revenue across 340+ funnels.
        </p>

        <h3>The 7-Figure Email Sequences</h3>
        <p>
          The exact welcome series, nurture sequence, and cart-abandonment flows that
          drive 40%+ of total funnel revenue. Every email is pre-written with proven
          subject lines and copy. Load them into your ESP and let them run.
        </p>

        <h3>Automation Workflows</h3>
        <p>
          Visual flowcharts for every stage: lead capture → qualification → nurture →
          sale → upsell → referral. Not concepts — the actual workflows you copy into
          your CRM. If/then logic, delay timers, tag triggers — all mapped out.
        </p>

        <h3>The Funnel Math Spreadsheet</h3>
        <p>
          Before you spend a dollar on ads, know your numbers. This spreadsheet models
          your customer acquisition cost, lifetime value, and break-even point across
          different traffic scenarios.
        </p>

        <h3>Step-by-Step Implementation Guide</h3>
        <p>
          Takes you from "I have nothing" to "my funnel is live and accepting payments."
          No theory, no fluff — just "click here, paste this, publish that."
        </p>

        <h2>It fits in a lot of places</h2>

        <ul class="sl-list">
          <li><strong>As your primary funnel system.</strong> Tired of paying month after month <em>forever</em> just to keep your funnel running? Slash your costs and make the Blueprint your primary conversion system.</li>
          <li><strong>As your backup system.</strong> Want to keep your existing tools, but need a backup when those go down? Don't pay in perpetuity for something on standby.</li>
          <li><strong>As educational material.</strong> You get the templates. Dissect them, study them, modify them, examine them from the inside.</li>
          <li><strong>For launches and promotions.</strong> Need a fast funnel for a new offer, a flash sale, or a seasonal campaign? Deploy a proven template in hours, not weeks.</li>
          <li><strong>For client work.</strong> Set up a white-label funnel for your clients, completely separate from your own marketing. No licensing headaches.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 id="testimonials">But does it actually work?</h2>

        <blockquote>
          "We implemented the Blueprint on a Friday afternoon and had our first automated
          sale by Monday morning. Within 90 days our funnel was doing $47K/month — more
          than our entire sales team was producing before."
          <cite>— Jamie Rodriguez, Founder at ScaleUp Agency</cite>
        </blockquote>

        <p>
          Jamie isn't an outlier. We hear stories like this every week. Not because the
          Blueprint contains some secret formula, but because most businesses are starting
          from such a low baseline that <em>any</em> systematic approach dramatically
          outperforms "figure it out as we go."
        </p>

        <blockquote>
          "I was paying an agency $4,000/month to manage my funnels. After the Blueprint,
          I realized I could do 90% of it myself. Cancelled the agency, implemented the
          templates, and actually got <em>better</em> results."
          <cite>— Sarah Kim, Coach & Course Creator</cite>
        </blockquote>

        <blockquote>
          "The automation workflows alone saved me 20 hours a week. I stopped manually
          sending follow-ups and just let the system run. Revenue went up 40% in the
          first month."
          <cite>— Marcus Chen, SaaS Founder</cite>
        </blockquote>

        <h2>Why are we giving this away?</h2>

        <p>
          We sell advanced funnel tools and services. The Blueprint is the front door.
          When you implement it and see results — and you will — some percentage of you
          will want to go further. You'll want the advanced templates, the done-for-you
          setup, the optimization services.
        </p>

        <p>
          That's how we make money. Not by gatekeeping basic knowledge behind a paywall,
          but by giving you the system for free, letting you prove it works, and being
          there when you're ready to scale.
        </p>

        <h2 id="faq">Frequently asked questions</h2>

        <h3>What exactly do I get?</h3>
        <p>
          The complete system: page templates, email sequences, automation workflows, the
          funnel math spreadsheet, and the implementation guide.
        </p>

        <h3>Do I need technical skills?</h3>
        <p>
          No. If you can use a Google Doc, you can implement this. Click-by-click
          walkthroughs with screenshots for every step.
        </p>

        <h3>What if I already have a funnel?</h3>
        <p>
          Even better. Most people find 2–3 high-leverage optimizations immediately.
          The email sequences and automation workflows alone are worth the download.
        </p>

        <h3>How is this different from courses?</h3>
        <p>
          This isn't a course. No video library. No weekly calls about mindset. You get
          the exact assets that generated $12M+ in revenue, ready to deploy.
        </p>

        <h3>Is it really free?</h3>
        <p>
          Yes. No credit card, no trial, no bait-and-switch. We make money when you succeed
          and choose to upgrade. The Blueprint is how we earn your trust.
        </p>

        <h3>Can I use this for my clients?</h3>
        <p>
          Absolutely. The templates are yours to use however you'd like — for your own
          business, for client projects, or as a starting point for something entirely new.
        </p>

        {/* Bottom spacing for mobile sticky button */}
        <div class="h-24 lg:hidden" />

      </article>
    </div>

    {/* ══ RIGHT: sticky CTA card ══ */}
    <aside class="sl-sidebar hidden lg:block" id="get-started">
      <div class="sticky" style="top: 6rem;">
        <div class="sl-card">

          <p class="sl-card-label">Free Download</p>
          <p class="sl-card-title">Get the $100K Funnel Blueprint</p>
          <p class="sl-card-body">
            Templates, email sequences, automation workflows, and a step-by-step implementation guide — sent straight to your inbox.
          </p>

          <div class="sl-card-form">
            <LeadCaptureForm
              client:load
              formTags={formTags}
              submitLabel="Get Instant Access"
            />
          </div>

          {/* Testimonial */}
          <div class="sl-card-testimonial">
            <div class="sl-card-stars">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" /></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" /></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" /></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" /></svg>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <p class="sl-card-quote">"Implemented on Friday, first sale by Monday. $47K/month within 90 days."</p>
            <p class="sl-card-cite">Jamie Rodriguez, ScaleUp Agency</p>
          </div>

        </div>

        <p class="sl-card-sub">
          By providing my information, I agree to receive communications and accept the <a href="/terms">Privacy Policy</a>. Unsubscribe anytime.
        </p>
      </div>
    </aside>

  </div>

  {/* Mobile Sticky Form Sheet */}
  <div class="lg:hidden">
    <MobileFormSheet
      client:load
      formTags={formTags}
      submitLabel="Get Instant Access"
      termsHtml={termsHtml}
    />
  </div>

  {/* Footer */}
  <footer slot="footer" class="sl-footer">
    <div class="sl-footer-inner flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-2 text-xs text-foreground-muted">
      <p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} {siteConfig.name}. All rights reserved.</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-5">
        <a href="/terms" class="hover:text-foreground transition-colors">Privacy</a>
        <a href="/terms" class="hover:text-foreground transition-colors">Terms</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ── Two-column layout ── */
  .sl-layout {
    display: flex;
    max-width: 72rem; /* max-w-6xl — matches homepage */
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem 0;
  }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .sl-layout {
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
      padding-right: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
  .sl-content {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }
  .sl-sidebar {
    flex: 0 0 380px;
    margin-left: 2.5rem;
    padding-top: 3rem;
  }

  /* ── Hero ── */
  .sl-hero {
    padding-top: 3.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .sl-title {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.08;
    color: var(--foreground);
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .sl-title {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
    }
  }
  .sl-subtitle {
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
    font-size: 1.1875rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--foreground-muted);
    max-width: 620px;
  }

  /* ── Sidebar Card ── */
  .sl-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    background: var(--background);
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }
  .sl-card-label {
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--brand-500);
  }
  .sl-card-title {
    margin-top: 0.375rem;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: var(--foreground);
  }
  .sl-card-body {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--foreground-muted);
  }
  .sl-card-form {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .sl-card-testimonial {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .sl-card-stars {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1px;
  }
  .sl-card-stars svg {
    width: 0.875rem;
    height: 0.875rem;
    color: #f59e0b;
  }
  .sl-card-quote {
    margin-top: 0.375rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--foreground-secondary);
  }
  .sl-card-cite {
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    color: var(--foreground-muted);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .sl-card-sub {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--foreground-muted);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .sl-card-sub a {
    text-decoration: underline;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* ── Product Figure ── */
  .sl-figure {
    margin: 2.5rem 0;
  }
  .sl-product-frame {
    background: var(--secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .sl-product-frame img {
    width: 280px;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
  }
  .sl-figure figcaption {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--foreground-muted);
  }

  /* ── Footer ── */
  .sl-footer {
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .sl-footer-inner {
    max-width: 72rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* ── Responsive ── */
  @media (max-width: 1279px) {
    .sl-sidebar {
      flex: 0 0 320px;
    }
  }
</style>

<style is:global>
  /* ── Editorial Typography ── */
  .sales-letter {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--foreground-secondary);
    padding-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  .sales-letter p {
    margin-top: 1.25em;
  }
  .sales-letter p:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }
  .sales-letter strong {
    color: var(--foreground);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .sales-letter em {
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .sales-letter a {
    color: var(--foreground);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    text-decoration-thickness: 1.5px;
  }
  .sales-letter a:hover {
    color: var(--brand-500);
  }
  .sales-letter h2 {
    font-size: 1.625rem;
    line-height: 1.25;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--foreground);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-top: 2.75em;
    margin-bottom: 0.15em;
  }
  .sales-letter h3 {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--foreground);
    margin-top: 2em;
    margin-bottom: 0.1em;
  }
  .sales-letter blockquote {
    margin-top: 1.5em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5em;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--brand-500);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--foreground);
  }
  .sales-letter blockquote cite {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 0.5em;
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--foreground-muted);
  }
  .sales-letter figure {
    margin-left: 0;
    margin-right: 0;
  }
  .sales-letter .not-prose,
  .sales-letter .not-prose * {
    font-size: revert;
    line-height: revert;
    margin: revert;
  }
  .sales-letter ul.sl-list {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 1.25em;
    margin-top: 1em;
  }
  .sales-letter ul.sl-list li {
    margin-top: 0.75em;
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .sales-letter {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
    }
  }
</style>
